  <description>
    <p>
      Experience the ultimate modernization of DOOM-3-BFG with RBDOOM-3-BFG!

      This source port brings cutting-edge technology to the classic, featuring PSX-style and 8/16-bit retro rendering modes, immersive CRT filters, enhanced global illumination PBR lighting, and realistic blood effects. 
      Designed for both retro enthusiasts and casual gamers, RBDOOM-3-BFG delivers a complete overhaul while staying true to the original gameplay.
      This version reintroduces the iconic classic flashlight as an option, letting you experience the suspense and atmosphere of DOOM 3 just as you remember it.
      
      Now requiring Vulkan and supporting Wayland, it's the definitive way to relive DOOM 3 with a fresh, modern twist.
    </p>
